name bxcalc
category Package
revision 78793
shortdesc Extend the functionality of the calc package
longdesc This package bundle consists of the following packages:
longdesc bxcalcize: To make calc expressions available in more places.
longdesc bxcalcux: To add user-defined units to the calc syntax. In
longdesc addition, this bundle provides the bxcalc package, which simply
longdesc loads the above-mentioned packages internally.
